data.description: All the charm you could want in desirable Colleton Park. This quaint neighborhood boasts Rocking Chair Front porches and rear garages. This mint condition home has a great floor plan with beautiful master in back, deluxe master bathroom and 2 master walk in closets. Two nice size guest bedrooms in front and large bonus room upstairs. Additionally a walk in attic for plenty of storage. The main living level has a cozy living room with gas fireplace, dining room and supersize kitchen and breakfast area. The side porch overlooks fenced yard. ( this home is on a double lot. ) Owners added many upgrades including hardwood floors throughout except bonus, Replaced both HVAC units, Changed to gas with Rinnai hot water system, Added fence and new roof. This is a must see home.
